==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Desudation
<hw>Des`u*da"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>desudatio</ets>, fr. <ets>desudare</ets> to sweat greatly;
<ets>de</ets> + <ets>sudare</ets> to sweat.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A sweating; a profuse or morbid sweating, often succeeded by an
eruption of small pimples.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Desuete</ent>⟦br⟧
